               <msContents>
                  <summary>Sword of the Trinity, ሠይፈ፡ ሥላሴ፡, Journey to Heaven, Blessing of Abunä Yared, History of Priest Yared, Wise of the Wise, Booklet of prayer that came down from heaven for a nobleman in the land of the Afrǝgi, Prayer of the Twelve Disciples, Prayer of the Disciples for Forgiveness of Sin, Sword of Divinity, ሠይፈ፡ መለኮት፡, Mystagogia, ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡, God of the Luminaries, እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘብርሃናት፡, Prayer: I take refuge, ተማኅፀንኩ፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

