                      <title>Blessing of Abunä Yared, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10245Yared">Yāred</persName>
                     </title>
                      <incipit xml:lang="gez">ቡራኬ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ያሬድ፡ ዘይትበሀል፡ ለለዕለቱ፡ ስብሐት፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ዘፈጠረ፡ ሰማያተ፡ ወምድረ፡ ኪነ፡ ወተግባረ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                      </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="16r" to="18v" facs="017">Fols 16r–18v</locus>
                      <title>History of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10245Yared">Yāred</persName></title>
                      <textLang mainLang="am"/>
                      <note>This story, which is slightly different from what is in his <foreign xml:lang="gez">ገድል፡</foreign>, is composed in Amharic, but the beginning is in Gǝ‘ǝz</note>
                      <incipit xml:lang="gez">ዝታሪክ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ያሬድ፡ ባሕታዊ፡ ወድንግል፡ ዘይነግር፡ ኵነቶ፡ ፅንሰቶ፡ ወልደቶ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ያሬድ፡ በተወለደል፡ በ፯፡ ዓመቱ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                      </msItem>
